Package nl.naturalis.geneious.note

Enum NaturalisField

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NaturalisField>
      • nl.naturalis.geneious.note.NaturalisField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<NaturalisField>
    public enum NaturalisField
extends Enum<NaturalisField>
    Symbolic constants for all fields that can be included in a NaturalisNote. Each field represents a single annotation in a Geneious document.

      • cast

        <T> T cast​(Object val)
        Casts the provided object (presumably already processed by a NoteFactory to an object of this field's datatype. Since the note factory probably already returned the right datatype, this is just an extra type check. If the casting throws a ClassCastException, an error is logged and this method returns null.
